ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectCanada - Kazakhstan ** Co-operation in the Peaceful Uses of Nuclear Energy **
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to sign, or to delegate powers to sign, on behalf of Canada, subject to ratification, the AGREEMENT between the Government of Canada and the Government of the REPUBLIC OF KAZAKHSTAN for CO-OPERATION IN THE PEACEFUL USES OF NUCLEAR ENERGY.
